episodes.natural_language:
Initial client contact on September 30, 2025, with Tonya Dunn regarding a motor vehicle accident that occurred on September 24, 2025 (DOA 9/24/2025). Tonya Dunn is a 1972 birth, reachable at 502-381-0282, with Social Security Number 402-04-0723. She resides at 12 Modern Way, Louisville, KY 40206. She reports that she was stopped at a flashing red light on Newburg Road at the light before entering I-264 West when she was rear-ended. No police department (PD) responded at the scene, and she indicated she would text with updates.

The incident is noted with BI: Root and PIP through State Farm, though she has not spoken with State Farm yet. The client’s vehicle is a 2007 Chevrolet Impala. She currently has no health insurance. She went to St. Mary and Elizabeth on Bluegrass for care, and no EMS was involved. Injuries reported include thoracic pain and neck pain. The outreach was conducted by Justin on September 30, 2025.
